Description: HiPAC-SHP receiver polling agent
 Scans the local network with arp-scan, logs into HiPAC receivers over SSH,
 captures the receiver_cli TUI screen and reports receiver/node readings to the
 central HiPAC-SHP dashboard.
 .
 Includes a local, password-protected web UI (port 8080) for setting the site
 name, polling interval, excluded IPs, server URL/token and SSH details.
